OL,3,CKiller who stabbed Gateshead mother 27
OL,4,Ctimes jailed
OL,6,FA man has been sentenced to life in
OL,7,Fprison with a minimum of 17 and a half
OL,8,Fyears for the murder of a woman in
OL,9,FGateshead.
OL,11,F39-year-old Ben Hughes admitted to
OL,12,Fkilling 37-year-old Laura Robson, was
OL,13,Fstabbed 27 times during an attack at a
OL,14,Fhouse in Appledore Close Greenside in
OL,15,FJuly 2024.
OL,17,FHughes pleaded guilty to her murder at
OL,18,Fa court hearing in November 2024 and
OL,19,Fhad been remanded in custody until
OL,20,Ftoday's sentencing.
