OL,6,FThe court heard how the mother-of-
OL,7,Fthree had come to Hughes' flat in
OL,8,FGreenside near Ryton on 22 July 2024.
OL,9,FThe pair had known each other for just
OL,10,Fa few days after meeting through a
OL,11,Ffriend.
OL,13,FThe court was also told how that same
OL,14,Fnight, Laura had sent a text to a
OL,15,Ffriend to say things were not good and
OL,16,Fthat she was returning home.
OL,18,FHowever, a few minutes later a
OL,19,Fneighbour of Hughes called the police
OL,20,Fto report hearing loud screams and
OL,21,Fcries help coming from Hughes' flat.
