OL,6,FThe neighbour heard Laura calling out
OL,7,Fthat she was about to die going to die
OL,8,Fand was going to "bleed out", with
OL,9,FHughes replying that she was going to
OL,10,Fdie anyway and that nobody was coming
OL,11,Fto help her.
OL,13,FLaura's body was found in the front
OL,14,Froom of the house by Emergency
OL,15,Fservices. She was declared her dead at
OL,16,Fthe scene.
