OL,6,F"I keep asking myself why would he do
OL,7,Fthat to my daughter, to take her life
OL,8,Fthe way he did. Life without Laura is
OL,9,Fa battle everyday"
OL,11,FSpeaking following the hearing,
OL,12,FDetective Chief Inspector Rebecca
OL,13,FFenney, of Northumbria Police, said:
OL,14,F"First and foremost, I would like to
OL,15,Fpay tribute to Laura's family and
OL,16,Floved ones for the strength they have
OL,17,Fshown in the past six months.
